landing.bio: I'm studying Computer Engineering at Iowa State University, and I have a love of all things tech. My interests lie in comupter architecture and embedded sytems.

experience.aboutWork: Led large groups of students, guiding learning in calculus. Employed active learning strategies. Provided expretise about the subject material.
Led small group sessions. Guided work through calculus problems in a variety of courses. Kept lesson plans.

interests.paragraphOne: Outside of school, I enjoy listening to and playing music, whether it be guitar, drums, or bass.
interests.paragraphTwo: I also love to be outside enjoying nature.
